### Authentication Tests

### 1. Đăng ký tài khoản mới
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New User",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 2. Đăng nhập
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 3. Lấy thông tin bản thân (Me) - Cần token
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### User CRUD Tests

### 4. Lấy tất cả users
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users

###

### 5. Lấy user theo ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/USER_ID_HERE

###

### 6. Tạo user mới
POST http://localhost:3001/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "age": 25
}

###

### 7. Cập nhật user
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "age": 26
}

###

### 8. Xóa user
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/users/USER_ID_HERE

###

### Project Tests (Relationship Demo)

### 9. Tạo project mới
POST http://localhost:3001/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Project",
  "description": "Testing user-project relationship",
  "status": "pending",
  "owner": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

###

### 10. Lấy tất cả projects (với populate owner)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/projects

###

### 11. Lấy project theo ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE

###

### 12. Cập nhật project
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in-progress",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

###

### 13. Xóa project
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE
